LCD PICTURES

Hand-drawn on an unexpanded Amiga 500 (1 Meg) by Ludovic Colacino Dias.
Enhanced (with permission) on an Amiga 1200 (68030/40/50/4) by Christian Kemp.

Copyright (C)1994 Colacino Dias Ludovic.
Additional Copyright (C)1995 Christian Kemp.
All Rights Reserved.
The pictures are freely distributable as long as this text is included
and no profit is made.  (Prices must not exceed 2$/disk or 40$/CD)

Contact me for any reason :
Christian Kemp
52, BD Patton
L-2316 Luxembourg

The originals were in Lores 32 colors.  I modified them to Multiscan 256
colors (Arbre and Tableau) and 16 colors (Wing_Football) with PPaint 4.
Effects used (and abused) include "Blur" and "Randomize".
Converted to JPEG (24 bit) using Transition.

Click below to see the pictures (requires WB3.0+ and a JPEG datatype).
@{"Arbre.JPG" LINK Arbre.JPG/main}
@{"Tableau.JPG" LINK Tableau.JPG/main}
@{"Wing_Football" LINK Wing_Football.JPG/main}
{You should have a >256 color WB to get optimal results!)

